akia}}\n| {{flag|Australia}},<br />{{flag|Germany}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2002\n| 15th\n| [[Odessa]]\n| {{flag|Ukraine}}\n| 20\n| 18\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| {{flag|Belarus}},<br />{{flag|Germany}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2003\n| 16th\n| [[Uppsala]]\n| {{flag|Sweden}}\n| 23\n| 22\n| {{flag|Germany}}\n| {{flag|South Korea}},<br />{{flag|Poland}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2004\n| 17th\n| [[Brisbane]]\n| {{flag|Australia}}\n| 26\n| 24\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| {{flag|Germany}},<br />{{flag|Slovakia}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2005\n| 18th\n| [[Winterthur]]\n| {{flag|Switzerland}}\n| 25\n| 23\n| {{flag|Germany}}\n| {{flag|Belarus}},<br />{{flag|United States}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2006\n| 19th\n| [[Bratislava]]\n| {{flag|Slovakia}}\n| 26\n| 24\n| {{flag|Croatia}}\n| {{flag|South Korea}},<br />{{flag|Germany}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2007\n| 20th\n| [[Seoul]]\n| {{flag|South Korea}}\n| 22\n| 21\n| {{flag|Australia}}\n| {{flag|South Korea}}-2,<br />{{flag|New Zealand}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2008\n| 21st\n| [[Trogir]]\n| {{flag|Croatia}}\n| 21\n| 21\n| {{flag|Germany}}\n| {{flag|Croatia}},<br />{{flag|New Zealand}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2009\n| 22nd\n| [[Tianjin]]\n| {{flag|China}}\n| 27\n| 27\n| {{flag|South Korea}}\n| {{flag|Austria}},<br />{{flag|New Zealand}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2010\n| 23rd\n| [[Vienna]]\n| {{flag|Austria}}\n| 23\n| 23\n| {{flag|Singapore}},<br />{{flag|Austria}},<br />{{flag|New Zealand}},<br />{{flag|South Korea}}\n| {{flag|Germany}},<br />{{flag|Chinese Taipei}},<br />{{flag|Iran}},<br />{{flag|Australia}},<br />{{flag|Slovakia}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| [[IYPT 2011|2011]]\n| 24th\n| [[Tehran]]\n| {{flag|Iran}}\n| 21\n| 21\n| {{flag|South Korea}},<br />{{flag|Austria}},<br />{{flag|Germany}}\n| {{flag|Chinese Taipei}},<br />{{flag|Iran}},<br />{{flag|Slovakia}},<br />{{flag|Singapore}},<br />{{flag|Belarus}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| 2012\n| 25th\n| [[Bad Saulgau]]\n| {{flag|Germany}}\n| 28\n| 28\n| {{flag|South Korea}},<br />{{flag|Iran}},<br />{{flag|Singapore}}\n| {{flag|Belarus