a]] \u2013 former Dean and Professor of the [[Colombo Medical School|Medical Faculty]], [[University of Colombo]], and National Coordinator, Health Systems Research, Ministry of Health<ref name=\"Kottegoda\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nation.lk/2007/12/16/events.htm |title=Top anti-doping expert speaks on 'Ethics in Sports Medicine' |publisher=Nation.lk |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref>\n* [[Sanath Lamabathusooriya]] {{post-nominals|MBE}} \u2013 former Dean of the [[Colombo Medical School|Medical Faculty]], [[University of Colombo]] and Emeritus Professor of Paediatrics (note: also listed in Medicine)\n* [[Sri Lankan honours system|Vidya Jyothi]] [[Janaka de Silva]] \u2013 Senior Professor of Medicine and Former Dean of the Faculty of Medicine, [[University of Kelaniya]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rcclassof72.lk/old_site/inside_pages/d.htm |title=Prof Hithanadura Janaka De Silva |publisher=Rcclassof72.lk |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref> and Director of the Postgraduate Institute of Medicine, University of Colombo (note: also listed in Medicine)\n* [[Sri Lankan honours system|Vidya Jyothi]] [[A. W. Mailvaganam]] \u2013 former Dean of Faculty of Science, [[University of Ceylon]]\n* [[S. Mahalingam (veterinarian)|S. Mahalingam]] \u2013 former Dean of the Faculty of Veterinary Sciences, [[University of Peradeniya]] and Professor of Veterinary Clinical Sciences\n* [[Ajith P. Madurapperuma]] \u2013 Former Dean and Senior Lecturer, Faculty of Information Technology, [[University of Moratuwa]]\n* [[Sunitha Wickramasinghe]] {{post-nominals|FRCP}} \u2013 Deputy Dean of the [[Imperial College School of Medicine]] and Professor of Haematology<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sundaytimes.lk/090913/Plus/plus_15.html |title=Prof Sunitha Wickramasinghe |publisher=Sundaytimes.lk |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref>\n* [[David de Kretser]] {{post-nominals|AC|KStJ}} \u2013 former Associate Dean of the Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences, [[Monash University]] (note: als