aman Gunatilake]] {{post-nominals|FRCP}} <small>[[Ceylon College of Physicians|FCCP]]</small> \u2013 Professor of Medicine, [[University of Sri Jayewardenepura]]<ref name=\"Saman\">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailynews.lk/2002/01/07/new13.html |title=Induction ceremony of the President |publisher=Dailynews.lk |date=2002-01-07 |accessdate=2011-09-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604234155/http://www.dailynews.lk/2002/01/07/new13.html |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref> (note: also listed in Medicine)\n* [[Nalin de Silva]] \u2013 Professor of Mathematics, Department of Mathematics, [[University of Kelaniya]]\n* [[Suri Ratnapala|A. Suri Ratnapala]] \u2013 Professor of Law, T.C. Beirne School of Law, [[University of Queensland]]\n* [[Nihal Jayawickrama]] \u2013 former Professor of Law at [[University of Hong Kong]] and Ariel F Sallows Professor of Human Rights at [[University of Saskatchewan]] (note: also listed in lawyers)\n* [[D. N. Samarasekera]] {{post-nominals|FRCS}} \u2013 Professor of Surgery, Head of the Department of Surgery, University of Colombo<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rcclassof72.lk/old_site/inside_pages/d.htm |title=Samarasekera Dharmabandhu Nandadeva Dr |publisher=Rcclassof72.lk |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/medicine/ext_pages/surgery/samarasekara.htm |title=Prof. D.N.Samarasekera |publisher=Cmb.ac.lk |date=2005-12-08 |accessdate=2012-02-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301165746/http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/medicine/ext_pages/surgery/samarasekara.htm |archivedate=2012-03-01 }}</ref>\n* [[Chandima Gomes]] \u2013 Professor of Electrical Engineering, [[Universiti Putra Malaysia]] and Head of the Centre for Electromagnetic and Lightning Protection Malaysia<ref>[[Chandima Gomes]]</ref>\n* [[R. K. W. Goonesekera]] \u2013 Professor of Law, [[Ahmadu Bello University]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sundaytimes.lk/980405/news5.html |title=VIP Complex problem gets complicated |publisher=Sundaytimes.lk |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref>\n* [[Asantha Cooray]] \u2013 Associate Professor, Department of Physics and Astronomy, [[University of California, Irvine]] and a leading researcher in the field of [[Cosmology]] and [[theoretical astrophysics]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cooray.org |title=Asantha R. Cooray |publisher=Cooray.org |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref>\n* [[Brendon Gooneratne]] \u2013 Head and Senior Lecturer, Department of Parasitology, [[University of Ceylon]], [[Peradeniya]]<ref name=\"Gooneratne\"/> (note: also listed in Authors)\n* [[Murugesapillai Maheswaran]] \u2013 Professor Emeritus of Mathematics, University of Wisconsin Stevens Point at Wausau,<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.uwsp.edu/mathsci/Pages/faculty/mMaheswaran.aspx |title = M Maheswaran &#124; University of Wisconsin Stevens Point at Wausau}}</ref> formerly Professor and Head, Department of Mathematics, [[University of Peradeniya]].\n\n==Scientists==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:*;\" | Name\n! style=\"width:65%;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notability\n! style=\"width:*;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Reference(s)\n|-\n| {{sortname|Mohan|Munasinghe}}\n| Physicist, academic, economist \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Ranjan|Ramasamy}}\n| Immunologist, biochemist, Chairman [[National Science Foundation of Sri Lanka|National Science Foundation]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|A. M.|Mubarak}}\n| Director Industrial Technology Institute, former Director, [[National Science Foundation of Sri Lanka|National Science Foundation]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Ray|Jayawardhana}}\n| [[Astronomer]], [[author]], professor [[University of Toronto]], Canada Research Chair in Observational Astrophysics \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lankajournal.com/?p=6029 |title=Ray in Canada's Top 40 List |publisher=Lankaj