om/index.php/media-center/related-news/102-harshana-rajakaruna-president-of-liberal-youth-guild-was-invited-and-attended-theexecutive-committee-meeting-of-the-iflry-which-was-held-in-timisoara-romania |title=Harshana Rajakaruna attended the Executive Committee meeting of the IFLRY in Romania |publisher=Idlsrilanka.com |date=2011-07-25 |accessdate=2012-02-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216023158/http://www.idlsrilanka.com/index.php/media-center/related-news/102-harshana-rajakaruna-president-of-liberal-youth-guild-was-invited-and-attended-theexecutive-committee-meeting-of-the-iflry-which-was-held-in-timisoara-romania |archivedate=2015-02-16 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.lakbimanews.lk/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2743%3Aunp-appoints-wpc-harshana-rajakaruna-as-convenor-of-ypa&Itemid=56 UNP appoints WPC Harshana Rajakaruna as convenor of YPA]{{Dead link|date=April 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Mayors===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:*;\" | Name\n! style=\"width:65%;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notability\n! style=\"width:*;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Reference(s)\n|-\n| {{sortname|V. R.|Schockman}}\n| [[Mayor of Colombo]] (1938&ndash;1939)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|S.|Sellamuttu}}\n| [[Mayor of Colombo]] (1951)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>[http://www.dailynews.lk/2010/02/15/fea07.asp Gift out of a challenge accepted with fortitude] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130221050426/http://www.dailynews.lk/2010/02/15/fea07.asp |date=2013-02-21 }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Omer|Kamil}}\n| [[Mayor of Colombo]] (1999&ndash;2002)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Prasanna|Gunawardena}}\n| [[Mayor of Colombo]] (2002&ndash;2006)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Cathiravelu|Ponnambalam}}\n| [[List of Mayors of Jaffna|Mayor of Jaffna]] (1950&ndash;1951)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|