]] (1992&ndash;2011)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{cite web|last=Athas |first=Iqbal |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/080504/Columns/sitreport.html |title=Columns - Situation Report |publisher=Sundaytimes.lk |date=4 May 2008|accessdate=10 September 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Athas |first=Iqbal |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/080504/Columns/sitreport.html |title=Senior officers decorated for unblemished service |publisher=Sundaytimes.lk |date=4 May 2008|accessdate=10 September 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|A.|Kumaresan}}\n| [[Air Vice Marshall]], Director Planning \u2013 [[Sri Lanka Air Force]] \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Shirantha|Goonatilake}} {{KIA}}\n| [[Air Commodore]], Commanding Officer \u2013 [[No. 1 Wing SLAF|No. 1 Flying Training Wing]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Rohan|Pathirage}}\n| [[Air Vice Marshall]], Director Electronics and Telecommunications Engineering \u2013 [[Sri Lanka Air Force]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>[http://www.airforce.lk/org/dete/dete.htm Directorate of Electronics and Telecommunications Engineering, SLAF] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201133131/http://www.airforce.lk/org/dete/dete.htm |date=February 1, 2009 }}</ref>\n|}\n\n===[[Ceylon Defence Force]]===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:*;\" | Name\n! style=\"width:65%;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notability\n! style=\"width:*;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Reference(s)\n|-\n| {{sortname|John Lionel|Kotalawela}}\n| [[Prime Minister of Sri Lanka|Prime Minister of Ceylon]] (1953&ndash;1956), Member of [[Parliament of Ceylon|Parliament]] - [[Dodangaslanda Electoral District|Dodangaslanda]] (1947&ndash;1959), Commanding Officer of the [[Ceylon Light Infantry]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|T. G.|Jayewardene}}\n| Member of the [[State Council of Ceylon]] (1933&ndash;1936), Commanding Officer of the [[Ceylon Light Infantry]]\n| style=\"text-ali