ar]] {{post-nominals|FRCP}} \u2013 first Professor of Medicine, [[University of Ceylon, Peradeniya]]\n* [[Saman Kelegama]] \u2013 Executive Director, Institute of Policy Studies of Sri Lanka and former President of the Sri Lanka Economic Association<ref>[http://www.businesstoday.lk/article.php?article=2469 Dr Saman Kelegama Appointed To Colombo Stock Exchange Board]</ref>\n* [[K. N. Jayatilleke]] \u2013 Head of the Department of Philosophy at the [[University of Ceylon]] and Professor of Philosophy\n* [[Kollupitiye Mahinda Sangharakkhitha Thera]] \u2013 Professor and Head of the Buddhist and Pail Faculty of the [[University of Kelaniya]]<ref name=\"Sangharakkhitha Thera\"/> (note: also listed in Prelates)\n* [[Rohan Abeyaratne]] \u2013 Quentin Berg Professor of Mechanics and CEO/Director of the [[Singapore\u2013MIT alliance|SMART Centre]], [[Massachusetts Institute of Technology]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://18.80.2.252/people/index.html?id=1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110703191930/http://18.80.2.252/people/index.html?id=1 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2011-07-03 |title=MIT Department of Mechanical Engineering - People |publisher=18.80.2.252 |accessdate=2011-09-10 }}</ref>\n* [[Nalin Kulatilaka]] \u2013 Wing Tat Lee Family Professor of Management and Research Director of Institute for Leading in a Dynamic Economy, [[Boston University]]\n* [[Gihan Wikramanayake]] \u2013 Professor of Computer Science and Director, [[University of Colombo School of Computing]]\n* [[Janek Ratnatunga]] \u2013 former Head of the School of Commerce, [[University of South Australia]] and Professor of Accounting\n* [[Sri Lankan honours system|Vidya Jyothi]] [[Rezvi Sheriff]] \u2013 Senior Professor of Medicine, Director of the Post Graduate Institute of Medicine, [[University of Colombo]]\n* [[Vela Velupillai|Kumaraswamy \"Vela\" Velupillai]] \u2013 Professor of Economics, Department of Economics, [[University of Trento]]\n* [[Milroy Paul]] <small>[[Membership of the Royal Co